'''提內耳氏徵象'''<ref>{{cite web |title=【范姜治澐醫師】淺談腕隧道症候群 |url=https://tw.wen8health.com/article/446 |website=wen8health健康新聞網 |accessdate=2020-05-14 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227153543/https://tw.wen8health.com/article/446 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=晚上配戴手腕托加上電針灸治療可以有效改善腕管綜合症患者的症狀嗎？ |url=https://www.hkiim.cuhk.edu.hk/ceim/tc/synopsis/detail/acupuncture-and-related-therapies/208 |website=香港中文大學醫學院 |accessdate=2020-05-14 |archive-date=2020-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920212532/https://www.hkiim.cuhk.edu.hk/ceim/tc/synopsis/detail/acupuncture-and-related-therapies/208 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{Lang-en|Tinel sign}}）是一种測試[[神经|神经]]是否受到刺激或發炎的方法，{{Le|叩診|Percussion (medicine)}}輕敲神经损伤部位可引起刺痛或{{tsl|en|Paresthesia|感覺異常}}。命名取自[[法国|法国]][[神经学家|神经学家]]{{le|朱爾斯·提內耳|Jules Tinel}}（1879-1952）<ref>Tinel, J., Nerve wounds. London: Baillère, Tindall and Cox, 1917</ref><ref>Tinel, J. (1915) Le signe du fourmillement dans les lésions des nerfs périphériques. Presse médicale, 47, 388-389</ref><ref>Tinel, J. (1978) The "tingling sign" in peripheral nerve lesions (Translated by EB Kaplan). In: M. Spinner M (Ed.), Injuries to the Ma jor Branches of Peripheral Nerves of the Forearm. (2nd ed.) (pp 8-13). Philadelphia: WD Saunders Co</ref>。

以[[腕隧道症候群|腕隧道症候群]][[手腕|手腕]]的[[正中神经|正中神经]]壓迫為例，提內耳氏徵象常為「陽性」，受試者[[拇指|拇指]]、[[食指|食指]]、[[中指|中指]]和半边[[无名指|无名指]]感到刺痛。提內耳氏徵象有時也被稱為'''叩診遠端刺痛'''（{{lang|en|Distal tingling on percussion}}），在[[體感|體感神經]]修復的階段，可以預期這個遠端徵象會跟著改善<ref>{{cite journal|title=At which stage of sensory recovery can a tingling sign be expected? a review and proposal for standardization and grading|pages=298–308|issn=0894-1130|journal=Journal of Hand Therapy: Official Journal of the American Society of Hand Therapists|volume=12|issue=4|date=1999-10|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10622196|accessdate=2019-02-13|author=C. Spicher, G. Kohut, J. Miauton|pmid=10622196|archive-date=2014-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102122713/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/10622196|dead-url=no}}<!-- Spicher, C., Kohut, G. & Miauton,  J. At which stage of sensory recovery can a tingling sign be expected? A review and proposal for standardization and grading. J Hand Ther, 1999, 12:298-308--></ref>。

儘管最常用於腕隧道症候群，提內耳氏徵象是一個廣義術語，用於{{le|跗隧道症候群|Tarsal tunnel syndrome}}或{{le|肘隧道症候群|Cubital tunnel syndrome}}也可呈現陽性反應。

